{"tid":1309624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[宣傳]7.21港島東遊行, 回歸港島戰線","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:38:47.000Z","uid":240516,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1d82b406d247fb7bcaf30df404dc6e71923ab8","tid":1309624,"uid":240516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"[宣傳]7.21港島東遊行, 回歸港島戰線<br />\n<br />\n起步時間: 15:30<br />\n預定路線: 鰂魚涌公園二期-渣華道-英皇道-維園<br />\n途經北角警署, 北角政府合署, 廉政公署總部, 民建聯總部<br />\n(有待不反對通知書確認)<br />\n<br />\n目的: 七大訴求(5+2) <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n6. 承諾不推行社會信用評分制度<br />\n7. 拆除所有監控燈柱<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"73a281f6d1332eb395012814e017cfff42b85eb6","tid":1309624,"uid":276216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"終點響維園？之後有乜活動"},{"pid":"2da095463255641ce79229179402af56df2a9cd9","tid":1309624,"uid":240516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73a281f6d1332eb395012814e017cfff42b85eb6","tid":1309624,"uid":276216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"終點響維園？之後有乜活動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"當日19:30民陣係金鐘有集會, 各位遊行完可以轉移過去"},{"pid":"51e3a4ffc57208fca5673be43bfe6e8cd88fbdd9","tid":1309624,"uid":240516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"da5bc1933e1e4b29144b3fe6db4c6bd88401939e","tid":1309624,"uid":150761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3f2267dd624ee47f3f01ccc529eddc055b2dfcfc","tid":1309624,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GpRAUPyK0W0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGpRAUPyK0W0&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTU